msgid "Freeze Before"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../effects_and_filters/video_effects/motion/freeze.rst:67
msgid "If checked, freezes the video from the start of the clip to the set :guilabel:`Freeze at` position. Default is **off**"
msgstr ""

